room_title: Escape room "Reactor Meltdown" by Harrison Street Escape Room in Bettendorf
room_description: The Quad Cities Nuclear Generating Station is experiencing a core meltdown. You and your team must find a power source strong enough to start Dr. Jamieson's Fusion Reactor. This action will create a Plasma Dome over the Quad Cities and protect the area from radiation. You have only one hour...
